headline: Macerich's Q1 FFO & Revenues Beat Estimates, Occupancy Dips Y/Y
summary: MAC's Q1 results reflect healthy leasing, driving same-center NOI and higher base rent re-leasing spreads. Yet, occupancy declines and costs rise year over year.
